ecember 16, 2019 |accessdate=December 19, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| January 2, 2020\n|[[Houston Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor|Best Supporting Actor]]\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[Independent Spirit Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/2019/11/indie-spirit-awards-2020-nominations-complete-list.html |title=The Lighthouse, Uncut Gems Lead 2020 Indie Spirit Nominations |website=Vulture |first=Zoe |last=Haylock |date=November 21, 2019 |accessdate=November 28, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[35th Independent Spirit Awards|February 8, 2020]]\n|[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n| Robert Eggers\n| {{nominated}} \n|-\n|[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Male Lead|Best Male Lead]]\n| Robert Pattinson\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n|[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Male|Best Supporting Male]]\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n|[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Editing|Best Editing]]\n|<nowiki/>Louise Ford\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n|[[Independent Spirit Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]]\n| Jarin Blaschke\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | Indiana Film Journalists Association<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-indiana-film-journalists-association-ifja-winners|website=NextBestPicture|date=December 16, 2019|title=The 2019 Indiana Film Journalists Association (IFJA) Winners| accessdate=December 18, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\" | December 16, 2019\n| Best Film\n|''The Lighthouse''\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Original Screenplay\n| Robert Eggers & Max Eggers\n| {{runner-up}}\n|- \n| Best Supporting Actor\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Original Vision Award\n| Robert Eggers\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Las Vegas Film Critics Society<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-las-vegas-film-critics-society-lvfcs-winners|title=\nThe 2019 Las Vegas Film Critics Society (LVFCS) Winners|website=NextBestPicture|date=December 13, 2019|accessdate=December 9, 2019}}</ref>\n| December 13, 2019\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[London Film Critics' Circle]] Awards<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/awards/parasite-wins-london-critics-awards-joaquin-phoenix-renee-zellweger-1203486577/|title='Parasite' Tops London Film Critics' Circle Awards|accessdate=31 January 2020}}</ref>\n| January 30, 2020\n| British / Irish Actor of the Year\n| Robert Pattinson\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | North Carolina Film Critics Association<ref>{{cite web| url=https://ncfilmcritics.org/?p=903| title=2019 North Carolina Film Critics Association Awards Nominations| publisher=NCFCA| date=December 27, 2019| accessdate=December 27, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | January 3, 2020\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Jarin Blaschke\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"8\" | North Dakota Film Society<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-north-dakota-film-society-ndfs-winners|title=\nThe 2019 North Dakota Film Society (NDFS) Winners|website=NextBestPicture|date=January 18, 2020|accessdate=January 18, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"8\" | January 18, 2020\n| Best Picture\n|''The Lighthouse''\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| Robert Eggers\n| {{nominated}} \n|-\n| Best Actor\n| Robert Pattinson\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| Willem Dafoe\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| Robert Eggers & Max Eggers\n| {{nominated}}\n|- \n| Best Cinematography\n| Jarin Blaschke\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Craig Lathrop, Ian Greig\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n|<nowiki/>Louise Ford\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Oklahoma Film Critics Circle<ref>{{cite web|url=https://awardswatch.com/oklahoma-film-critics-circle-ofcc-winners/|title=Oklahoma Film Critics Circle (OFCC) winners|website=AwardsWatch|date=December 15, 2019|accessdate=December 19, 2019}}</ref>\n| December 15, 2019\